### CREATE employee
POST http://localhost:1000/employee-api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Samhita",
    "email": "samhita@gmail.com",
    "mobile": "7995519098",
    "designation": "Manager",
    "companyName": "TCS"
}

### READ all employees
GET http://localhost:1000/employee-api/employees

### UPDATE employee
PUT http://localhost:1000/employee-api/employees/samhita@gmail.com
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Sam",
    "email": "samhita@gmail.com",
    "mobile": "7995519098",
    "designation": "Manager",
    "companyName": "Infosys"
}

### DELETE employee
DELETE http://localhost:1000/employee-api/employees/samhita@gmail.com